740
00:38:41,360 --> 00:38:42,600
Bukankah awak yang cakap

741
00:38:43,400 --> 00:38:43,960
kena berlakon

742
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:44,560
baik-baik?

743
00:38:46,120 --> 00:38:47,280
Kita baru berkahwin,

744
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:48,760
kena sentiasa bercumbu-cumbu.

745
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:53,920
Jadi, kita hanya boleh tidur di atas katil yang sama.

746
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:11,000
Awak pakai pakaian luar dan naik katil saya?

747
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:18,240
Saya memang tidur begini semasa di rumah.

748
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:20,280
Jika sayang tak biasa,

749
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,200
cuba sesuaikan dirilah.

750
00:39:32,120 --> 00:39:33,080
Betul cakap sayang,

751
00:39:33,960 --> 00:39:35,520
saya patut sesuaikan diri.

752
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:51,080
Awak tertekan rambut saya.

753
00:40:18,920 --> 00:40:20,000
Eh,

754
00:40:21,440 --> 00:40:23,480
kandi buah Kediaman Shen memang sedap.

755
00:40:23,640 --> 00:40:25,160
Saya tak habis-habis nak makan.

756
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:31,400
Sedaplah.

757
00:40:34,960 --> 00:40:35,880
Awak nak makan?

758
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:49,280
Awak...

759
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:52,120
Pak Zhong!

760
00:40:52,640 --> 00:40:53,440
Tukarkan ia!

761
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:56,160
Tukarkan semuanya!

